txt.en: 'Ever wonder how a Rock got so far from home? My dear Rune-keeper friend and I parted ways to go on our own adventures, and he recently mailed me a great deal of Eastern Gondor tokens. Do you want some?
'Trust me, there's many more where this came from. Come on back if you need them!'
By completing this quest, you will receive a Eastern Gondor tokens allowance.
